title: JavaZone 2020 CFS
body: JavaZone 2020 Call For Speakers is open.

title: JavaZone 2020 Sessions
body:
JavaZone 2020 sessions are not available until after the call for papers closes and the programme committee has had time to go through them.

Once they are available we will switch the app over to 2020 and they will replace the 2019 sessions in the app.

title: Current Testing
body: We are currently testing the session lists, session details and info view.
